* [[HP-UX]] (Hewlett-Packard)
* [[OpenVMS]] (originally Digital Equipment Corporation, now Hewlett-Packard)
* [[Solaris (operating system)|Solaris]] ([[Sun Microsystems]])
* [[UnixWare]] ([[Univel]])
* [[IRIX]] (For a short time [[Silicon Graphics]] offered CDE as an alternative to [[IRIX Interactive Desktop|IID]]{{Citation needed|date=February 2010}})

