      <comment>Undid revision 427308067 by [[Special:Contributions/Polisher of Cobwebs|Polisher of Cobwebs]] ([[User talk:Polisher of Cobwebs|talk]])</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox Book | &lt;!-- See [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Novels]] or [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Books]] --&gt;
