      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox company|
| company_name   = Cantor Fitzgerald, L.P.
| company_logo   = [[Image:Cantor Fitzgerald logo.png|200px|]]
| company_type   = [[Private company|Private]]
| foundation     = 1945
| location       = [[New York City, New York]], [[United States]]
| key_people     = Howard W. Lutnick &lt;small&gt;(Chairman &amp; CEO)&lt;/small&gt;&lt;br&gt;Shawn Matthews &lt;small&gt;(CEO)&lt;/small&gt;
| industry       = [[Investment|Investment Services]] |
