* Most Stolen Bases: 75, [[Kenny Lofton]] (1996)
* Most Wins: 31, [[Jim Bagby, Sr.]] (1920)
* Lowest ERA: 1.16, [[Addie Joss]] (1908)
* Strikeouts: 348, [[Bob Feller]] (1946)
