      <text xml:space="preserve">{{About|encoding and decoding a digital data stream}}
A '''codec''' is a device or [[computer program]] capable of [[encoder|encoding]] and/or [[Decoding methods|decoding]] a [[digital]] [[data stream]] or [[signal (information theory)|signal]].&lt;ref&gt;{{cite web |url=https://www.microsoft.com/windows/windowsmedia/player/faq/codec.mspx |title=Using codecs |publisher=Microsoft |accessdate=2009-12-21}}&lt;/ref&gt;&lt;ref&gt;{{cite web |url=